76561198273190585,Recommended,254440,31853350,Posted: 19 May,all,Regelian92,"If you love the age old game of pool and you want a good 3D virtually real game of pool for your PC look no further. Whether its 8 ball, 9 ball, tournament play, single match, or endurance Pool Nation has you covered. Play in one of many locations (in game of course) from all around the world. Before each game you will see breathtaking scenery, neon lights, exotic locations, and objects so realistic you will start to think that you are really there. There are pool stick upgrades, new ball sets and decals to unlock. Steam achievements that will make you feel proud when you get them. An online PVP mode and singles mode with AI oppenents. The tutorials teach you how to do some truly classic trick shots and there is a helpful tracer line that shows you what will happen if you shoot now (which can be disabled if you prefer a challenge). You will need the trick shots to get some of the achievements. But if you truly enjoy pool then it's just part of the fun.  There are some glitched out pool games out there but this one is definitely worth buying."
